plyTime":"2018-03-03T17:00:33.000Z","msg":"神山係咪要book 左山上住宿先  再搞登山證？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T17:31:52.000Z","msg":"一日得100人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79c85e000ac0f6697ed6b823b6fed53cdc48549f","tid":579450,"uid":164523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T02:40:42.000Z","msg":"上年7月去左神山 朝早去 我地係包車入去 路可以車入 冇行到啲咩不過真係空氣好好 景好靚 車入上到頂朋友仔唔多舒服 可能太高掛～ 山腳係未入去前有間餐廳 係我沙巴去咁多日食既第二好食 唔貴 拍得住香港小炒～<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/04/103948_d3d024b637db74be549a9c29449eb5a2.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F04%2F103948_d3d024b637db74be549a9c29449eb5a2.jpeg&h=83f14f60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n個日太大霧唔係幾靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f568aad58aab31fe508c92fca4dfb97bf6f8e91d","tid":579450,"uid":164523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T02:43:54.000Z","msg":"食既方面<br />\n上網搵下有幾間冰室都好好食 好易搵（唔記得個名）大茄來食下海鮮咁 啊炎叻沙都好好食 <br />\n雞飯就不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 對於我地講真係好難食 同食雞胸冇分別"},{"pid":"269182c480594fb358a1218c477ad2c284c0d2d9","tid":579450,"uid":127894,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T02:58:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>上神山係幾開心既 不過真係要有準備</blockquote>神山係咪要book 左山上住宿先  再搞登山證？</blockquote><br />\n係 book 左個床位先 上網有成套買 全包連個鋼索 4000 兩日一夜 吾包鋼索好似3000<br />\n btw, 果陣一推門入房 有個鬼妹換緊衫 立即好尷尬地講 sorry"},{"pid":"c2af42ee206aff6263a338fdaf91c20544d389aa","tid":579450,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T12:24:25.000Z","msg":"浮潛好似最好"},{"pid":"79116a341012629853ee1b1779e5b9140938ee14","tid":579450,"uid":117856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1